---
title: Chargrilled Pork Steak & Honey Haloumi with Roast Pumpkin, Goat Cheese & Radish Salad
description: Nothing beats a good chargrilled pork steak. Paired with lip-smacking honey haloumi, roast pumpkin and creamy
goat cheese, it's a winning barbeque meal. No barbie? No worries. Just follow our tips for cooking on the stove or in the oven!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chargrilled-pork-steak-honey-haloumi-f5057534.jpg
